PN,31801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FA case of suicide following domestic
OL,8,Fabuse where both the victim and
OL,9,Fsuspect were aged under 18 has been
OL,10,Fincluded in official police data for
OL,11,Fthe first time in England and Wales.
OL,13,FIt was among 150 suspected cases where
OL,14,Fabuse victims ended their lives in the
OL,15,Fyear to March 2025.
OL,17,FThese figures were published in
OL,18,FTuesday's annual report of the
OL,19,FDomestic Homicide Project, which
OL,20,Fanalyses police recorded domestic
OL,21,Fhomicides.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FAccess to violent pornography and
OL,8,F"toxic influencers" online may be
OL,9,Ffuelling abuse cases among teenagers
OL,10,Faged 16 to 19, says national policing
OL,11,Flead for domestic abuse, Assistant
OL,12,FCommissioner Louisa Rolfe.
OL,14,FA higher proportion of this
OL,15,Fdemographic were victims of domestic
OL,16,Fabuse compared to those aged 25 and
OL,17,Folder in the year to March 2025,
OL,18,Faccording to the annual Crime Survey
OL,19,Ffor England and Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FAcross all age groups, there has been
OL,8,Fa higher proportion of police recorded
OL,9,Fdomestic homicides where a victim took
OL,10,Ftheir own life after suffering abuse,
OL,11,Fcompared to those where a partner
OL,12,Fkilled the victim.
OL,14,FIn the five years of the annual
OL,15,FDomestic Homicide Project, 414 cases
OL,16,Fwere intimate partner homicide, 227
OL,17,Fwere adult familial homicide, 553 were
OL,18,Fsuicide following domestic abuse, 131
OL,19,Fwere unexpected deaths, 86 child
OL,20,Fdeaths and 41 were classified as other.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FThere have been four reported cases of
OL,8,Fsuicides where the victim was under 16
OL,9,Fand the perpetrator was over 18 `
OL,10,Fthree an adult family member, and one
OL,11,Fan intimate partner, the project's
OL,12,Ffigures show.
OL,14,FCommenting on Tuesday's report,
OL,15,FAssistant Commissioner Rolfe said:
OL,16,F"People are now much more likely to
OL,17,Faccess violent pornography which
OL,18,Fnormalises violence and behaviour in a
OL,19,Frelationship, and particularly non-
OL,20,Ffatal strangulation, (which is) hugely
OL,21,Fdangerous.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,F"We see the connection between the
OL,8,Fsort of sense of toxic influencers
OL,9,Fonline and their sort of views that
OL,10,Fare promoted about women and women's
OL,11,Fstatus in society."
OL,13,FAssistant Commissioner Rolfe said some
OL,14,Fdetectives are overwhelmed by their
OL,15,Fworkload and, therefore, more likely
OL,16,Fto close cases as suicide without
OL,17,Ffurther investigation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,F"Investigators are dealing with
OL,8,Fsustained exposure to trauma because
OL,9,Fof the number of cases they're dealing
OL,10,Fwith," she said.
OL,12,F"We're seeing that sometimes that's
OL,13,Faffecting their investigative
OL,14,Fdecisions in terms of, if there's a
OL,15,Fcase that on a knife-edge, and it
OL,16,Fcould be dealt with as a
OL,17,Fstraightforward suicide, or it could
OL,18,Fbe a long, protracted investigation,
OL,19,Fwhen it's one of 20 or 30 cases on
OL,20,Ftheir books, (there is) the motivation
OL,21,Fto close it early."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
