PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FCampaigners want a new law to make
OL,8,Fsuicide following domestic abuse a
OL,9,Fspecific criminal offence separate
OL,10,Ffrom manslaughter, to make it easier
OL,11,Ffor juries to understand.
OL,13,FFrank Mullane from support service
OL,14,FAdvocacy After Fatal Domestic Abuse
OL,15,Fsaid: "We need a new law which
OL,16,Fseparates suicide from domestic abuse,
OL,17,Ffrom manslaughter.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,F"I'm speculating that the average
OL,8,Fjuror sees manslaughter as maybe a
OL,9,Fpunch-up in a car park, other types of
OL,10,Fkilling. I think if we separate
OL,11,Fsuicide from domestic abuse, it will
OL,12,Fhelp educate the public."
OL,14,FIn the past five years, there have
OL,15,Fbeen 17 cases where domestic abuse
OL,16,Fcharges have been brought after a
OL,17,Fvictim took their own life, three of
OL,18,Fwhich investigated possible
OL,19,Fmanslaughter.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
