PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FThere are expected to be seven more
OL,8,Fposthumous cases, and the number of
OL,9,Fthese investigations is expected to
OL,10,Frise.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIn total, 1,452 deaths linked to
OL,18,Fdomestic abuse were recorded over a
OL,19,Ffive-year period, and 347 deaths in
OL,20,Fthe year to March 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
