PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FThis is an increase of 85 deaths from
OL,8,Fthe previous year, most of which are
OL,9,Fsuspected suicides following domestic
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FPolice believe this is down to
OL,13,Fincreased recording of such cases
OL,14,Frather than a rise in the number of
OL,15,Fcrimes being committed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
