PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777479067
OL,3,CFirst suicide linked to teenage
OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,FMinister for Safeguarding and Violence
OL,8,FAgainst Women and Girls Jess Phillips
OL,9,Fsaid: "Every life lost to domestic
OL,10,Fabuse is a devastating tragedy, and my
OL,11,Fthoughts are with families and loved
OL,12,Fones left grieving.
OL,14,F"I welcome this important report,
OL,15,Fwhich highlights the link between
OL,16,Fdomestic abuse and suicide, and
OL,17,Freinforces the need for tougher action
OL,18,Fto stop perpetrators causing harm.
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
