OL,4,Crelationship abuse recorded in England
OL,5,Cand Wales
OL,7,F"Our Violence Against Women and Girls
OL,8,FStrategy sets out how we are rooting
OL,9,Fout the causes of domestic abuse-
OL,10,Frelated deaths and deploying the full
OL,11,Fpower of the state to crack down on
OL,12,Fthese vile crimes."
OL,14,FHow to get help if you are struggling
OL,15,Fwith your mental health
OL,17,FSupport is available if you are a
OL,18,Fvictim of domestic violence
